      "description": "Looking for an affordable ride or a solid little project? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward, budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a fixer-upper with potential. It\u2019s priced to reflect its age and condition, and for the right buyer it could be a great way to get on the road without spending a fortune. If you want something honest, simple, and easy on the wallet, come take a look.",
